The '''Cimarrones de Sonora Fútbol Club Premier''' play in the [[Liga Premier de México|Liga Premier]] in [[Hermosillo]], [[Sonora]], [[Mexico]] and are the official reserve team for [[Cimarrones de Sonora]]. The games are held in the city of [[Hermosillo]] in the [[Estadio Miguel Castro Servín]].

