{{Infobox football tournament | logo = | founded = 2015–16 | region = [[Nepal]] | number of teams = 10 (2017) | current champions =[[Nepal Army Club]] | most successful team =[[Nepal Army Club]] 2 times | current = [[2018 Jhapa Gold Cup]] | nextseason = | prevseason = 2017 }}
'''Jhapa Gold Cup''' (lang.Nepali) '''झापा गोल्डकप''' is a football tournament held in [[Jhapa]]. It is held at the Jhapa Rangsala stadium in [[Jhapa]], [[Nepal]]. Many national and international clubs play in the Jhapa Gold Cup.
==History== Jhapa Gold Cup started on 2016 year. This first tournament won the Nepal Army club.
