{{Infobox football biography | name = Yohann Tihoni | image = | caption = | fullname = Yohann Tihoni<ref>{{cite web|title=Squad lists for the FIFA Confederations Cup Brazil 2013|url=https://www.fifa.com/mm/document/tournament/competition/02/10/38/80/fcclop_neutral.pdf|publisher=Fédération Internationale de Football Association (FIFA)|accessdate=20 June 2013|format=PDF|date=7 June 2013}}</ref> | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1994|07|20|df=y}} | birth_place = [[Tahiti]] | height = {{height|m=1.78}} | position = [[Midfielder#Attacking midfielder|Attacking midfielder]] | currentclub = [[AS Roniu]] | clubnumber = | youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = | years1 = 2012– | clubs1 = [[AS Roniu]] | caps1 = | goals1 = | nationalyears1 = 2011 | nationalteam1 = [[Tahiti national under-17 football team|Tahiti U17]] | nationalcaps1 = 5 | nationalgoals1 = 3 | nationalyears2 = 2015– | nationalteam2 = [[Tahiti national under-23 football team|Tahiti U23]] | nationalcaps2 = 3 | nationalgoals2 = 3 | nationalyears3 = 2013– | nationalteam3 = [[Tahiti national football team|Tahiti]] | nationalcaps3 = 2 | nationalgoals3 = 0 | club-update = | nationalteam-update = 20:57, 6 July 2015 (UTC) }} '''Yohann Tihoni''' (born 20 July 1994) is a soccer player from [[Tahiti]] currently playing for [[AS Roniu]] and for the [[Tahiti national football team]]. He was part of the Tahitian squad at the [[2013 FIFA Confederations Cup]] in Brazil.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ftf.pf/?p=7016 |title=La liste des 23 Toa Aito pour le Brésil|language=French |trans-title=List of the 23 Toa Aito for Brasil |publisher=FTF|date=24 May 2013 |accessdate=24 May 2013}}</ref>
